  <summary date="2018-07-25T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Fairness in Liver Allocation Act of 2018

This bill requires the Organ Procurement and Transplantation Network to reform the criteria for liver allocation so that allocation is not based on the donor candidate's place of residence or listing, unless it is necessary to avoid wasting organs.</summary>
